{"tid":2070953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#381:46TV","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T17:29:09.000Z","uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"806767391f1deafe70baec29c7ebd17ed8b9d993","tid":2070953,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcKB489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcKB489.jpg&h=cd031b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2Kiy2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2Kiy2v.jpg&h=fe3286de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/neN4uAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FneN4uAP.jpg&h=cc6af112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乃木坂46TV 19號開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/atctwn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/46TIMES2019.jpg?fit=1200,630&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fatctwn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F46TIMES2019.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%2C630%26ssl%3D1&h=8f7b264a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[/center]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一至四期生在內，團體目前共有48名成員，而隊長為秋元真夏。其與2015年8月21日成立的櫸坂46、以及2019年2月11日自櫸坂46獨立的日向坂46，構成大型偶像組合系列「坂道系列」。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團名取自坐落東京都赤坂地區乃木坂的「SME乃木坂大樓」，該建築為所屬唱片公司日本索尼音樂的前辦公大樓之一。根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n乃木坂46 25thシングル『しあわせの保護色』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbOSoGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbOSoGb.jpg&h=e28b375b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山下美月1st写真集『忘れられない人』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTTDep3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTTDep3.jpg&h=9c3fba6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白石麻衣 写真集『パスポート』限定カバー版<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vb9Mttv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvb9Mttv.jpg&h=8532546f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDo9rfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDo9rfb.jpg&h=982344e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n与田祐希 2nd写真集『無口な時間』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp/@0_mall/book/cabinet/9619/2100011829619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp%2F%400_mall%2Fbook%2Fcabinet%2F9619%2F2100011829619.jpg&h=f3c7875e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋元真夏2nd写真集『しあわせにしたい』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E09mMtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE09mMtJ.jpg&h=fb4bd72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堀未央奈2nd写真集『いつかの待ち合わせ場所』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kCZaTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kCZaTy.jpg&h=90f8cb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表（最新）</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiwFp7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiwFp7s.jpg&h=a613c338&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEdDWed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEdDWed.jpg&h=2ee64564&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOdMkF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOdMkF0.jpg&h=772b3c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WnYbNH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WnYbNH.jpg&h=89f903c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYFCsk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYFCsk5.jpg&h=1e5a7602&s={SIZE}\" /></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fnogizaka46sort.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=3361b10b\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...不如幫襯某良心代購小店，詳情請向手足查詢。另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本<del>或中國</del>參加握手會、演唱會、見面會，但不要幻想會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pfYy3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pfYy3G.jpg&h=5fd6fbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ad9709df1c423dd1b7ae106d5d2f188d7e2835","tid":2070953,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"20:15頃 乃木坂電視台<br />\n秋元真夏・久保史緒里・斎藤飛鳥・鈴木絢音・遠藤さくら<br />\n<br />\n22:00頃 「熱闘！Nリーグ乃木雀」<br />\n<br />\n23:00頃 乃木坂電視台<br />\n金川紗耶・早川聖来・樋口日奈<br />\n<br />\n※放送内容が変更になる場合がございます"},{"pid":"df0e26e4e9759071dfc823f2b6f5b6281e2ae382","tid":2070953,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fo2015D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFo2015D.jpg&h=5b7e44ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醉愛牙櫻"},{"pid":"6e543da97c9ad48edc21ed10ac19ff00255c9169","tid":2070953,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"新人留名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRGX4ja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRGX4ja.jpg&h=7ae5193e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賀喜變咗做花瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f88187126bd76fa5c7950d036da0f5de27970fd","tid":2070953,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e543da97c9ad48edc21ed10ac19ff00255c9169","tid":2070953,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"新人留名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRGX4ja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRGX4ja.jpg&h=7ae5193e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賀喜變咗做花瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e11d9288addc8f30c8c8b5e1db15d23b26aeea","tid":2070953,"uid":21977,"like":0,"disli